{"title":"太阳照进众人家","authors":["李忠贞"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":2,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳照进众人家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳泉纺纱厂女工李忠贞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大柳树，开了花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳照进众人家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席就是红太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照得工人家里特别亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煤和铁，沉又沉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阎锡山在它压死人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党，解放军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领导众人翻了身。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁还重、煤还沉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸总说省了劲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我问爸爸为什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你上山，我刨炭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你妈在家做熟饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有吃有穿省了心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干活就觉不费劲。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"称一斤是十六两，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我心忘不了共产党。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十六两是一斤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有吃有穿不忘解放军。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注：沉又沉是重的意思。）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}